parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain tensioner can cause the timing chain to jump teeth, leading to engine damage, loss of power, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or hesitates
the engine locks or stalls
the vehicle goes into limp mode
the vehicle experiences a loss of power
the vehicle jerks or hesitates during acceleration
the vehicle has difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the accelerator pedal position sensor can cause the engine to suddenly run at slow idle speed or accelerate uncontrollably, leading to a loss of vehicle control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The engine speed does not respond to the accelerator pedal
the engine suddenly runs at slow idle speed
the engine accelerates uncontrollably
the vehicle surges forward
the RPM increases to 4

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body assembly can cause the engine to shut down unexpectedly, leading to a loss of vehicle control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The engine shuts down suddenly
the vehicle loses power
the engine speed does not respond to the accelerator pedal
the engine suddenly runs at slow idle speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unwanted vehicle acceleration can cause the vehicle to surge forward, leading to a loss of vehicle control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates uncontrollably
the RPM increases to 4
the vehicle surges forward
the back end of the vehicle starts to fishtail.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Fault and Sudden Engine Shutdown
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shutdown of the engine while driving can cause loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents, and potentially resulting in serious injury or death. Additionally, the failure can lead to costly repairs and towing fees.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or shudders while driving
the engine shuts down suddenly
the transmission fault warning appears on the dashboard
the vehicle cannot be started or jumpstarted
the vehicle stalls or loses power while driving.
